@startuml room_type_status

title RoomType — Ciclo de Vida do Status

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EEF2FF
  BorderColor #7070AA
  ArrowColor #555588
  FontSize 13
}
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam noteBorderColor #CCBB55

[*] --> ACTIVE : create()

ACTIVE   --> INACTIVE : deactivate()
ACTIVE   --> ARCHIVED : archive()

INACTIVE --> ACTIVE   : activate()
INACTIVE --> ARCHIVED : archive()

ARCHIVED --> ACTIVE   : restore()
ARCHIVED --> DELETED  : delete()

DELETED --> [*]

note right of ARCHIVED
  ARCHIVED não pode ir para INACTIVE.
  Lança InvalidStateException (422).
  Única origem válida para delete().
  restore() exige status == ARCHIVED.
end note

note right of DELETED
  Estado terminal (soft delete).
  Nenhuma transição permitida.
  Somente alcançável via ARCHIVED.
end note

@enduml
